snippet.title: Command & Conquer - Tiberium Alliances - Launch Trailer [Full-HD]
snippet.description:
Check Command & Conquer -- Tiberium Alliances out now for free: http://www.tiberiumalliances.com/ 

» Subscribe - http://bit.ly/phen-subscribe
» Facebook - http://www.facebook.com/TiberiumAlliances/
» Twitter - http://twitter.com/CnCAlliances/

Command & Conquer Tiberium Alliances introduces an all new way to play in the C&C universe with a browser-based, free to play strategy MMO game. In Command & Conquer Tiberium Alliances, your skills as a Commander will be put to the test as you enter the fight for resources and world domination.

Play it now for free!
http://www.tiberiumalliances.com/
